&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;VF3000 series manifold&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thread types: Rc(PT), NPT, NPTF, G(PF)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manifold types: B mount single base; S mount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maximum stations: 20 (B mount type); 10 (S mount type)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Common/Individual EXH&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Port sizes: 1/8, 1/4&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

